Instructions to open the simulation:
1. Press the build.zip file
2. Press the download button
3. Extract the build.zip into your desktop
4. Run the out.exe file inside of it

Instructions to read any of the source files I wrote:
1. Press the sources folder
2. Press any of the files inside
3. The files you see are the pertinent ones, all the others
are configurations, assets (shaders) and the likes
4. If you want to see the GPU programs
4.1 Press assets
4.2 Press shaders
4.3 Press either one of the four

Controls:
Mouse Wheel to select your algorithm
S to shuffle the set
A to sort the set
